Write a java program to swap two values without the use of 3rd variable.

Input format:

First input: an integer

Second input: an integer

Output format:

The output will be integers(swapped values)
Sample Input:

10

20

Sample Output:

20

10

import java.util.Scanner;
class Main
{
    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        //created an object for the Scanner function
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        
        //declaring 2 variables for the user inputs
        int a,b;
        
        //getting inputs for both the variables
        a = sc.nextInt();
        b = sc.nextInt();
        
        //Swapping of the 2 numbers without the 3rd variable
        a += b;
        b = a - b;
        a -= b;
        
        System.out.println(a);
        System.out.print(b);
    }
}
